<strong>Contact #{projectName project}
<div .row>
  <div .col-md-9 .col-lg-8>
    <p>
      Note: logged-in users can instead post
      <em>publicly
      at the
      <a href=@{ProjectDiscussionR (projectHandle project)}> project discussion page
      or elsewhere (such as discussions connected to wiki pages).
